                  <h1>Overview</h1>

<p>
  Intensive Journal workshops have helped survivors of trauma deal with
many painful and emotional issues.  Participants benefit from working in
a supportive environment protected by total privacy, and nurtured by a
group that provides an energy and momentum to move through issues.
</p>

<p>
  Our exercises help survivors access and work through feelings of pain
  and guilt, in a safe way; they are in control of how far their can move
  through an issue.  Through this process, they can gain clarity and
  insights as well as a sense of peace to move forward in life.
</p>
